data.description: Situated on a canal in SE Palm Bay, this 3 bedroom 2 bath split plan home provides  a tranquil retreat from the modern day hustle and bustle world.  The property is completely fenced and looks onto TREES!    The property features a remodeled kitchen, a large gathering area, 2 bedrooms and bath on one side and the primary suite on the other side of the home for privacy.  There is a screened porch on the back from which to take in the peaceful views.  There is tile and laminate floors throughout!    A/C, Fridge and Cedar fence installed approx 3 years ago. Roof and water treatment system about a year old.   Bring your pets and settle in, and ENJOY LIFE!
